OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FHarrods' compensation scheme for
OL,7,Fsurvivors of Mohamed Al-Fayed closed
OL,8,Ftoday, but those abused by the former
OL,9,Fowner say it did not go far enough,
OL,10,FITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FSurvivors of abuse by former Harrods
OL,14,Fowner Mohamed Al-Fayed have returned
OL,15,Fto the department store, many for the
OL,16,Ffirst time in decades, as its
OL,17,Fcompensation scheme closes - warning
OL,18,Fit has not delivered justice and
OL,19,Fcalling for those who enabled the
OL,20,Fabuse to be held accountable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
