OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FLindsay Mason, who worked as Al-
OL,7,FFayed's personal assistant in the late
OL,8,F1980s, said she was sexually assaulted
OL,9,Fand that he attempted to rape her.
OL,11,FReturning to Harrods, she described
OL,12,Fthe experience as overwhelming.
OL,14,F"Being in such close proximity to the
OL,15,Fplace that really had a devastating
OL,16,Fand irrevocable effect on my life...
OL,17,FI'm feeling very anxious," she said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
