OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FAl-Fayed, who died in 2023, is accused
OL,7,Fof abusing hundreds of women and girls
OL,8,Fover nearly four decades. Some
OL,9,Fsurvivors believe the true scale may
OL,10,Fbe even greater.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHarrods launched its compensation
OL,18,Fscheme last year after the wave of
OL,19,Fallegations came to light, setting
OL,20,Faside millions of pounds for victims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FThe company has said it is "deeply
OL,7,Fsorry" and has described the culture
OL,8,Funder Al-Fayed as one of "secrecy,
OL,9,Fintimidation and abuse".
OL,11,FMore than 200 people are understood to
OL,12,Fhave come forward ahead of the
OL,13,Fscheme's closure today.
OL,15,FFor Harrods, it represents an effort
OL,16,Fto address historic wrongdoing. But
OL,17,Ffor the survivors who I met today, it
OL,18,Ffalls short.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@FO]pD@ZOUqD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FJen Mills, who also worked for and was
OL,7,Fabused by Al-Fayed, said she refused
OL,8,Fto take part.
OL,10,F"It's preposterous that the very
OL,11,Fpeople who enabled these crimes are
OL,12,Fnow the very people that are running
OL,13,Fthat compensation scheme. So they are
OL,14,Fwell and truly marking their own
OL,15,Fhomework."
OL,17,FOthers argue the issue goes far beyond
OL,18,Fone individual.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,F"This is not a one-man situation,"
OL,7,Fsaid survivor Cheska Hill-Wood. "We
OL,8,Fwere almost put on a conveyor belt fed
OL,9,Finto this hell. And there has to be
OL,10,Faccountability for that."
OL,12,FOther survivors say the scheme has
OL,13,Foffered a meaningful option.
OL,15,FThey told ITV News they found the
OL,16,Fscheme supportive and that it provided
OL,17,Fsome closure without a lengthy legal
OL,18,Fprocess.
OL,20,FBut part of the associated paperwork
OL,21,Fhas raised concern.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@bO]rD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
