PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FParticularly, a form that requires
OL,7,Fthose receiving compensation to agree
OL,8,FHarrods no longer holds liability.
OL,10,FIn the small print, claimants are
OL,11,Fasked if they would assist the company
OL,12,Frecover costs from Al-Fayed's estate.
OL,14,FOne survivor described that request as
OL,15,F"strange", saying it appeared to
OL,16,Fsuggest Harrods begrudged making
OL,17,Famends.
OL,19,FShe also questioned why she should
OL,20,Fhelp - when she believes the company
OL,21,Fenabled the abuse she suffered.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FThe independent survivors' advocate,
OL,7,FJasvinder Sanghera, who has been hired
OL,8,Fby Harrods to help ensure the scheme
OL,9,Fis fair, said 200 women had come
OL,10,Fforward to make a claim.
OL,12,F"Many women will say to me it's not
OL,13,Fabout the money," she said. "It's
OL,14,Fabout being heard, being valued and
OL,15,Fbeing acknowledged and that's what
OL,16,Fredress is about."
OL,18,FShe added that survivors continue to
OL,19,Fhave options beyond the scheme,
OL,20,Fincluding ongoing support and legal
OL,21,Froutes.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@QO]uD@]OUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
