CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775012614
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner Al-
OL,4,CFayed say compensation falls short
OL,6,FFor those gathered outside Harrods
OL,7,Ftoday the scheme falls short.
OL,9,FThey want a full public inquiry and a
OL,10,Ffaster police investigation to ensure
OL,11,Fthose involved in enabling abuse are
OL,12,Fbrought to justice.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
